goal.ch:
"Define the groundwater flow in soils that are related to particular civil engineering projects;
‧ Introduction to fundamental laws and equations related to groundwater flows such as potential, heads, pore water pressure, discharge velocity and so on.
‧ Identify boundary conditions for solving groundwater problems mathematically in different approaches and apply to typical civil engineering design projects."

